					<span class="label"><a name="footnote10-13395_000_015">10.</a></span>
					<p class="">See Topical Guide, “<a href="https://www.lds.org/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ?lang=eng" target="_blank">Jesus Christ</a>.” In addition to text under that major heading, there are 57 subtitles about Him. For non-English editions of the scriptures, use Guide to the Scriptures.</p>
				</li><li class="footnote " id="footnote11-13395_000_015"><a name="11-13395_000_015"> </a>
					<span class="label"><a name="footnote11-13395_000_015">11.</a></span>
					<p class="">More than 2,200 listings are cited in those 18 pages of the Topical Guide.</p>
