					<span class="label"><a name="footnote13-13395_000_015">13.</a></span>
					<p class=""><span class="emphasis"><a href="http://www.lds.org/manual/teachings-joseph-smith/chapter-3">Teachings of Presidents of the Church: Joseph Smith</a></span> (2007), 49.</p>
				</li><li class="footnote " id="footnote14-13395_000_015"><a name="14-13395_000_015"> </a>
					<span class="label"><a name="footnote14-13395_000_015">14.</a></span>
					<p class="">See “<a href="http://www.lds.org/liahona/2000/04/the-living-christ-the-testimony-of-the-apostles-the-church-of-jesus-christ-of-latter-day-saints">The Living Christ: The Testimony of the Apostles</a>,” <span class="emphasis">Ensign</span> or <span class="emphasis">Liahona,</span> Apr. 2000, 2–3.</p>
				</li><li class="footnote " id="footnote15-13395_000_015"><a name="15-13395_000_015"> </a>
